  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and conquer a 100-floor roguelite dungeon in this cute but challenging card-battler RPG. Open card packs, change your class, customize your deck, equip accessories, and take on quests from quirky NPCs as you experience a charming story and engage in strategic turn-based battles against unique enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/f53db393fdaf10f24b260a12a21f2931.poster.avif?t=1734562493\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/f53db393fdaf10f24b260a12a21f2931.webm?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/f53db393fdaf10f24b260a12a21f2931.mp4?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategic card-battler combat</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face down a variety of enemies and challenging bosses, each with their own unique behaviors and mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase card packs with in-game gold, then arrange your deck. The cards you choose will determine your class; Each comes with their own unique perk!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize  your cards to your liking! Each card can be buffed up to three times with 15 different traits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip powerful accessories that complement your unique playstyle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/d250cffb8e14fd85b3da663d9bf2e175.poster.avif?t=1734562493\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/d250cffb8e14fd85b3da663d9bf2e175.webm?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/d250cffb8e14fd85b3da663d9bf2e175.mp4?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore and survive a 100-floor roguelite dungeon</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each room is procedurally generated and changes with every visit!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scour rooms for treasure chests, breakables, and hidden gold and health drops. The items you find can be used for crafting, customizing, or completing quests.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/0974ca29e65fa5efc31bf2236731dc0f.poster.avif?t=1734562493\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/0974ca29e65fa5efc31bf2236731dc0f.webm?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/0974ca29e65fa5efc31bf2236731dc0f.mp4?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience a charming story and quirky characters</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Aria find her older sister who has mysteriously vanished.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assist the locals in rebuilding and improving the town by taking on quests that feature humorous dialog.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and conquer a 100-floor roguelite dungeon in this cute but challenging card-battler RPG. Open card packs, change your class, customize your deck, equip accessories, and take on quests from quirky NPCs as you experience a charming story and engage in strategic turn-based battles against unique enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/f53db393fdaf10f24b260a12a21f2931.poster.avif?t=1734562493\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/f53db393fdaf10f24b260a12a21f2931.webm?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/f53db393fdaf10f24b260a12a21f2931.mp4?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategic card-battler combat</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face down a variety of enemies and challenging bosses, each with their own unique behaviors and mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase card packs with in-game gold, then arrange your deck. The cards you choose will determine your class; Each comes with their own unique perk!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize  your cards to your liking! Each card can be buffed up to three times with 15 different traits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip powerful accessories that complement your unique playstyle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/d250cffb8e14fd85b3da663d9bf2e175.poster.avif?t=1734562493\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/d250cffb8e14fd85b3da663d9bf2e175.webm?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/d250cffb8e14fd85b3da663d9bf2e175.mp4?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore and survive a 100-floor roguelite dungeon</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each room is procedurally generated and changes with every visit!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scour rooms for treasure chests, breakables, and hidden gold and health drops. The items you find can be used for crafting, customizing, or completing quests.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/0974ca29e65fa5efc31bf2236731dc0f.poster.avif?t=1734562493\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/0974ca29e65fa5efc31bf2236731dc0f.webm?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061850/extras/0974ca29e65fa5efc31bf2236731dc0f.mp4?t=1734562493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience a charming story and quirky characters</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Aria find her older sister who has mysteriously vanished.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assist the locals in rebuilding and improving the town by taking on quests that feature humorous dialog.</p></li></ul>",
